, peace and blessings be upon him, and gave the pledge of allegiance for embracing Islam. The next day he came with a fever and he said, \u201cCancel my pledge.\u201d The Prophet refused three times and he said, \u201cMedina is like a furnace. It\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42046,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/07\/23\/angels-curse-threat\/","url_meta":{"origin":40576,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Intimidation: Angels curse threatening Muslims","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever points an iron weapon at his brother, the angels surely curse him until he backs down, even if they were brothers from the same parents.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2616 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27299,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/03\/21\/believer-purified-by-illness\/","url_meta":{"origin":40576,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Believer purified by illness like iron in a fire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Azhar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the parable of the believer, when he is afflicted by illness or fever, is that of a piece of iron